## ScreenReaderClient.messages property

Array of stored messages. Messages are added to this array as soon as they arrive on the websocket, and can be removed by [ScreenReaderClient.clearMessages()](./assistive-playwright-client.screenreaderclient.clearmessages.md) and [ScreenReaderClient.waitForMessage()](./assistive-playwright-client.screenreaderclient.waitformessage.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
messages: string[];
```
